{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"removeAnnotations:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"NSArray<id<MLNAnnotation>>","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:Q$objc(cs)NSArray"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"annotations","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The array of annotation objects to remove. Objects in the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"array must conform to the ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" protocol.","type":"text"}]}],"name":"annotations"}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Removing annotation objects dissociates them from the map view entirely,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"preventing them from being displayed on the map. Thus you would typically","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"call this method only when you want to hide or delete the given annotations.","type":"text"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"sections":[],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/removeAnnotations:"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Removes an array of annotations from the map view, deselecting any selected"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"annotations in the array."}],"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":